Laura Menninger 
Subject: US v. Maxwell - 20 Cr. 330 - Letter re Minor Victim-3 
Date: Sat, 06 Nov 2021 03:56:27 +0000 
Attachments: Gov't_Letter_re_MV-3 junredacted].pdf; Gov't_Letter re_MV-3jproposed_redactions].pdf 
Chambers, 
Attached please find the Government's letter regarding Minor Victim-3, and a letter with proposed redactions. Pursuant 
to the Court's procedure, and unless otherwise ordered, the Government will file a redacted version on the docket once 
the defense notifies the Government whether it has any redactions. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
1 Saint Andrews Plaza 
New York, New York 10007 
EFTA00028203
